Control
├── id (UUID)
├── organization_id (FK)
├── control_id (e.g., "AC-1")
├── title
├── description
├── category (preventive, detective, corrective)
├── framework (SOC2, ISO27001, NIST, custom)
├── owner_id (FK - User)
├── frequency (continuous, daily, weekly, monthly, quarterly, annual)
├── last_tested_date
├── next_test_date
├── effectiveness_rating (1-5)
├── status (active, inactive, remediation_needed)
├── version_number
├── parent_version_id (FK - self-referencing)
├── created_at
└── updated_at